84
00:05:36,040 --> 00:05:37,480
If I do not put up a front,

85
00:05:37,720 --> 00:05:39,959
I am afraid I will not have peace.

86
00:05:40,120 --> 00:05:41,600
(They are dead.)

87
00:05:42,000 --> 00:05:43,360
(You still want to use them.)

88
00:05:44,040 --> 00:05:45,879
Are you not afraid
His Majesty will find out?

89
00:05:48,519 --> 00:05:50,000
