98
00:06:05,759 --> 00:06:06,800
No benefit at all.

99
00:06:07,399 --> 00:06:08,560
But once it is leaked,

100
00:06:09,120 --> 00:06:10,759
it will be detrimental to you.

101
00:06:11,199 --> 00:06:11,879
After all,

102
00:06:12,319 --> 00:06:13,879
we have

103
00:06:14,120 --> 00:06:15,759
quite a deep bond.

104
00:06:16,959 --> 00:06:17,759
But,

105
00:06:17,920 --> 00:06:19,160
please rest assured.

106
00:06:19,360 --> 00:06:20,000
Back then,

107
00:06:20,199 --> 00:06:21,800
thanks to your assistance

108
00:06:21,920 --> 00:06:23,800
and the princess's guidance.

109
00:06:24,360 --> 00:06:25,279
Late Lord of Zishang

110
00:06:25,600 --> 00:06:27,480
