111
00:06:28,079 --> 00:06:30,199
Even if he was to be torn to pieces,

112
00:06:30,920 --> 00:06:32,399
it would be fitting punishment.

113
00:06:33,439 --> 00:06:34,839
What does this have to do

114
00:06:35,079 --> 00:06:36,160
with us?

115
00:06:36,959 --> 00:06:37,680
My lord,

116
00:06:37,839 --> 00:06:38,959
